    "title": "The best wireless earbuds in 2026",
    "dek": "Sony's WF-1000XM6 set the high bar for noise cancelling, while the Soundcore Liberty 4 NC stays the budget champion under $100.",
    "image": "img/best-wireless-earbuds-2026.jpg",
    "imageAlt": "A pair of wireless earbuds in an open charging case",
    "imageCredit": "Illustration: GadgetPulse",
    "tags": ["earbuds", "audio", "Sony"],
    "body": [
      {"type":"p","text":"Earbuds split cleanly in 2026 between flagship noise-cancellers and genuinely good budget pairs. At the top, Sony's WF-1000XM6 leads the pack; under $100, Soundcore's Liberty 4 NC is hard to beat."},
      {"type":"h2","text":"The flagship pick"},
      {"type":"p","text":"The Sony WF-1000XM6 (released February 2026, around $330) offers class-leading active noise cancelling, comfort and multipoint pairing — at a price bump over its predecessor."},
      {"type":"h2","text":"The budget champion"},
      {"type":"ul","items":["Soundcore Liberty 4 NC (around $80-100) — adaptive ANC, multipoint, long battery; the safest all-rounder","Clip-on options like the Baseus Bowie MC2 for open-ear comfort during workouts"]},
      {"type":"h2","text":"What to look for"},
      {"type":"p","text":"Prioritize ANC that actually works on commutes, multipoint to pair a phone and laptop at once, a secure fit, and at least an IPX4 rating if you train with them."}
    ],
    "faq": [
      {"q":"What are the best wireless earbuds in 2026?","a":"The Sony WF-1000XM6 are widely rated best overall, with the Soundcore Liberty 4 NC the top budget pick under $100."},
      {"q":"Do budget earbuds have good noise cancelling in 2026?","a":"Yes — models like the Soundcore Liberty 4 NC offer effective adaptive ANC for around $80-100."}
    ],
    "sources": [
